      "id": "html-form-basics",
      "moduleId": "html-forms-media",
      "title": "Form Elements",
      "order": 1,
      "difficulty": "beginner",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- `<form>` wraps form elements\n- `<input>` for text fields, `<textarea>` for multi-line\n- `<label>` links to inputs via `for`/`htmlFor`\n- `<button type=\"submit\">` submits the form\n- `<select>` + `<option>` for dropdowns\n\n---\n\n# Form Elements\n\nForms are how users interact with websites - from search boxes to contact forms to login pages.\n\n## The Form Container\n\nEvery form starts with the `<form>` element:\n\n```html\n<form action=\"/submit\" method=\"POST\">\n  <!-- Form elements go here -->\n</form>\n```\n\n**Attributes:**\n- `action`: URL where form data is sent\n- `method`: HTTP method (GET or POST)\n- `name`: Form identifier\n\n## Text Inputs\n\n### Basic Text Field\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" placeholder=\"Enter username\" />\n```\n\n### Email Field\n```html\n<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" required />\n```\n\n### Password Field\n```html\n<input type=\"password\" name=\"password\" minLength=\"8\" />\n```\n\n### Multi-line Text (Textarea)\n```html\n<textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" cols=\"40\" placeholder=\"Your message...\"\n></textarea>\n```\n\n## Labels\n\nLabels improve accessibility and user experience:\n\n```html\n<!-- Method 1: Using for attribute -->\n<label htmlFor=\"email\">Email:</label>\n<input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" />\n\n<!-- Method 2: Wrapping input -->\n<label>\n  Username:\n  <input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" />\n</label>\n```\n\n**Why labels matter:**\n- Clicking label focuses the input\n- Screen readers announce the label\n- Better touch targets on mobile\n\n## Dropdowns (Select)\n\n```html\n<label htmlFor=\"country\">Country:</label>\n<select id=\"country\" name=\"country\">\n  <option value=\"\">Select a country...</option>\n  <option value=\"us\">United States</option>\n  <option value=\"uk\">United Kingdom</option>\n  <option value=\"ca\">Canada</option>\n</select>\n```\n\n### Multi-select\n```html\n<select name=\"skills\" multiple size=\"4\">\n  <option value=\"html\">HTML</option>\n  <option value=\"css\">CSS</option>\n  <option value=\"js\">JavaScript</option>\n</select>\n```\n\n## Submit Button\n\n```html\n<!-- Primary submit button -->\n<button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n\n<!-- Alternative -->\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" />\n\n<!-- Reset button -->\n<button type=\"reset\">Clear Form</button>\n\n<!-- Regular button (for JavaScript) -->\n<button type=\"button\" onClick={handleClick}>\n  Click Me\n</button>\n```\n\n## Complete Form Example\n\n```html\n<form action=\"/contact\" method=\"POST\">\n  <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"name\">Full Name *</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"text\"\n      id=\"name\"\n      name=\"name\"\n      required\n      placeholder=\"John Doe\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"email\">Email *</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      id=\"email\"\n      name=\"email\"\n      required\n      placeholder=\"john@example.com\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"subject\">Subject</label>\n    <select id=\"subject\" name=\"subject\" required>\n      <option value=\"\">Select a subject...</option>\n      <option value=\"general\">General Inquiry</option>\n      <option value=\"support\">Technical Support</option>\n      <option value=\"sales\">Sales</option>\n    </select>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"message\">Message *</label>\n    <textarea\n      id=\"message\"\n      name=\"message\"\n      rows=\"5\"\n      required\n      placeholder=\"How can we help you?\"\n    ></textarea>\n  </div>\n  \n  <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n</form>\n```\n\n## Form Best Practices\n\n1. **Always use labels** - Critical for accessibility\n2. **Validate on client side** - Use `required`, `minlength`, etc.\n3. **Validate on server side** - Never trust client validation alone\n4. **Group related fields** - Use `<fieldset>` and `<legend>`\n5. **Show clear errors** - Help users fix mistakes\n6. **Use appropriate types** - `type=\"email\"` shows right keyboard on mobile"
    },
    {
      "id": "html-input-types",
      "moduleId": "html-forms-media",
      "title": "Input Types",
      "order": 2,
      "difficulty": "beginner",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- `text`, `email`, `password`, `number`, `tel`, `url`\n- `checkbox`, `radio` for selections\n- `date`, `time`, `color`, `range` for specialized input\n- `required`, `minlength`, `pattern` for validation\n\n---\n\n# Input Types\n\nHTML5 introduced many specialized input types that improve user experience and validation.\n\n## Text-Based Inputs\n\n### Text\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" placeholder=\"Your name\" />\n```\n\n### Email\nShows email keyboard on mobile, validates format:\n```html\n<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" required />\n```\n\n### Password\nMasks characters:\n```html\n<input type=\"password\" name=\"password\" minLength=\"8\" />\n```\n\n### Number\nShows number keypad, enforces numeric input:\n```html\n<input type=\"number\" name=\"age\" min=\"18\" max=\"120\" />\n```\n\n### Telephone\nShows telephone keypad on mobile:\n```html\n<input type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"(555) 123-4567\" />\n```\n\n### URL\nValidates URL format:\n```html\n<input type=\"url\" name=\"website\" placeholder=\"https://example.com\" />\n```\n\n### Search\nShows search icon, may show clear button:\n```html\n<input type=\"search\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search...\" />\n```\n\n## Selection Inputs\n\n### Checkboxes\nUse for multiple selections:\n\n```html\n<fieldset>\n  <legend>Select your interests:</legend>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"interests\" value=\"tech\" />\n    Technology\n  </label>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"interests\" value=\"sports\" />\n    Sports\n  </label>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"interests\" value=\"music\" checked />\n    Music\n  </label>\n</fieldset>\n```\n\n### Radio Buttons\nUse for single selection from options:\n\n```html\n<fieldset>\n  <legend>Choose your plan:</legend>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"plan\" value=\"free\" checked />\n    Free\n  </label>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"plan\" value=\"pro\" />\n    Pro ($10/month)\n  </label>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"plan\" value=\"enterprise\" />\n    Enterprise ($50/month)\n  </label>\n</fieldset>\n```\n\n**Key difference:** Radio buttons with same `name` are mutually exclusive.\n\n## Specialized Inputs\n\n### Date\nShows date picker:\n```html\n<input type=\"date\" name=\"birthday\" min=\"1900-01-01\" max=\"2025-12-31\" />\n```\n\n### Time\n```html\n<input type=\"time\" name=\"meeting\" />\n```\n\n### Color\nShows color picker:\n```html\n<input type=\"color\" name=\"favoriteColor\" value=\"#ff0000\" />\n```\n\n### Range\nSlider control:\n```html\n<input type=\"range\" name=\"volume\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" />\n```\n\n### File\nFile upload:\n```html\n<input type=\"file\" name=\"avatar\" accept=\"image/*\" />\n```\n\n### Hidden\nInvisible field for server data:\n```html\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"userId\" value=\"12345\" />\n```\n\n## Validation Attributes\n\n### Required\nField must be filled:\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" required />\n```\n\n### Min/Max Length\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" minLength=\"3\" maxLength=\"20\" />\n```\n\n### Pattern (Regex)\n```html\n<!-- US Zip code -->\n<input type=\"text\" pattern=\"[0-9]{5}\" title=\"5-digit zip code\" />\n\n<!-- Alphanumeric only -->\n<input type=\"text\" pattern=\"[a-zA-Z0-9]+\" />\n```\n\n### Min/Max (for numbers)\n```html\n<input type=\"number\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" step=\"5\" />\n```\n\n### Placeholder\n```html\n<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Enter your name\" />\n```\n\n## Complete Registration Form\n\n```html\n<form action=\"/register\" method=\"POST\">\n  <h2>Create Account</h2>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"username\">Username *</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"text\"\n      id=\"username\"\n      name=\"username\"\n      required\n      minLength=\"3\"\n      maxLength=\"20\"\n      pattern=\"[a-zA-Z0-9_]+\"\n      placeholder=\"john_doe\"\n    />\n    <small>3-20 characters, letters, numbers, underscores only</small>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"email\">Email *</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"email\"\n      id=\"email\"\n      name=\"email\"\n      required\n      placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"password\">Password *</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"password\"\n      id=\"password\"\n      name=\"password\"\n      required\n      minLength=\"8\"\n      placeholder=\"Minimum 8 characters\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"age\">Age</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"number\"\n      id=\"age\"\n      name=\"age\"\n      min=\"13\"\n      max=\"120\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label htmlFor=\"website\">Website</label>\n    <input\n      type=\"url\"\n      id=\"website\"\n      name=\"website\"\n      placeholder=\"https://yourwebsite.com\"\n    />\n  </div>\n  \n  <fieldset>\n    <legend>Account Type *</legend>\n    <label>\n      <input type=\"radio\" name=\"type\" value=\"personal\" required checked />\n      Personal\n    </label>\n    <label>\n      <input type=\"radio\" name=\"type\" value=\"business\" />\n      Business\n    </label>\n  </fieldset>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"newsletter\" />\n    Subscribe to newsletter\n  </label>\n  \n  <label>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"terms\" required />\n    I agree to the Terms of Service *\n  </label>\n  \n  <button type=\"submit\">Create Account</button>\n</form>\n```\n\n## Input Type Quick Reference\n\n| Type | Use For | Mobile Keyboard |\n|------|---------|-----------------| |\n| `text` | General text | Text |\n| `email` | Email addresses | Email |\n| `password` | Passwords | Text (masked) |\n| `number` | Numeric values | Number |\n| `tel` | Phone numbers | Phone |\n| `url` | Web addresses | URL |\n| `search` | Search queries | Search |\n| `date` | Dates | Date picker |\n| `time` | Times | Time picker |\n| `color` | Colors | Color picker |\n| `range` | Sliders | - |\n| `file` | File uploads | - |\n| `checkbox` | Multiple selection | - |\n| `radio` | Single selection | - |\n| `hidden` | Server data | - |"
    },
