      "id": "html-media",
      "moduleId": "html-forms-media",
      "title": "Media Elements",
      "order": 3,
      "difficulty": "beginner",
      "content": "# Essential to know\n- `<video>` embeds video with `controls` attribute\n- `<audio>` embeds audio\n- `<iframe>` embeds external content (YouTube, maps)\n- `<figure>` + `<figcaption>` for media with captions\n\n---\n\n# Media Elements\n\nModern HTML makes it easy to embed videos, audio, images with captions, and external content.\n\n## Video\n\n### Basic Video Player\n```html\n<video src=\"video.mp4\" controls width=\"640\" height=\"360\">\n  Your browser doesn't support the video tag.\n</video>\n```\n\n### Video with Multiple Sources\nProvide multiple formats for browser compatibility:\n\n```html\n<video controls width=\"640\" poster=\"thumbnail.jpg\">\n  <source src=\"video.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n  <source src=\"video.webm\" type=\"video/webm\" />\n  <source src=\"video.ogv\" type=\"video/ogg\" />\n  \n  <p>Your browser doesn't support HTML video.</p>\n</video>\n```\n\n**Video Attributes:**\n- `controls` - Show play/pause buttons\n- `autoplay` - Start playing automatically (muted required in most browsers)\n- `loop` - Repeat when finished\n- `muted` - Start muted\n- `poster` - Image shown before play\n- `preload` - `auto`, `metadata`, or `none`\n\n### Video Best Practices\n```html\n<video\n  controls\n  width=\"640\"\n  preload=\"metadata\"\n  poster=\"video-thumb.jpg\"\n>\n  <source src=\"video.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n  \n  <!-- Fallback text -->\n  <p>\n    Your browser doesn't support HTML video.\n    <a href=\"video.mp4\">Download the video</a>.\n  </p>\n</video>\n```\n\n## Audio\n\nSimilar to video but for sound:\n\n```html\n<audio controls>\n  <source src=\"audio.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\" />\n  <source src=\"audio.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\" />\n  Your browser doesn't support the audio element.\n</audio>\n```\n\n**Audio Attributes:**\n- `controls` - Show play/pause/volume\n- `autoplay` - Start automatically\n- `loop` - Repeat\n- `muted` - Start muted\n- `preload` - Loading behavior\n\n## Images with Captions\n\n### Figure and Figcaption\n\nUse for images, videos, diagrams with captions:\n\n```html\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"chart.png\" alt=\"2024 Sales Chart\" width=\"600\" />\n  <figcaption>\n    Figure 1: Q4 2024 sales increased by 25% compared to Q3.\n  </figcaption>\n</figure>\n```\n\n### Video with Caption\n```html\n<figure>\n  <video controls width=\"640\">\n    <source src=\"tutorial.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n  </video>\n  <figcaption>\n    Tutorial: How to deploy your first website\n  </figcaption>\n</figure>\n```\n\n## Iframes\n\nEmbed external content like YouTube videos, Google Maps, or other websites:\n\n### YouTube Video\n```html\n<iframe\n  width=\"560\"\n  height=\"315\"\n  src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID\"\n  title=\"YouTube video player\"\n  frameBorder=\"0\"\n  allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n  allowFullScreen\n></iframe>\n```\n\n### Google Maps\n```html\n<iframe\n  src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=...\"\n  width=\"600\"\n  height=\"450\"\n  style=\"border:0\"\n  allowFullScreen\n  loading=\"lazy\"\n  referrerPolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"\n></iframe>\n```\n\n### Generic Iframe\n```html\n<iframe\n  src=\"https://example.com/external-page\"\n  width=\"800\"\n  height=\"600\"\n  title=\"External Content\"\n  sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin\"\n  loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n```\n\n**Iframe Attributes:**\n- `src` - URL to embed\n- `width/height` - Dimensions\n- `frameBorder` - Border (0 for none)\n- `allowFullScreen` - Allow fullscreen mode\n- `loading` - `lazy` for performance\n- `sandbox` - Security restrictions\n- `referrerPolicy` - Control referrer info\n\n## Picture Element (Responsive Images)\n\nServe different images based on screen size:\n\n```html\n<picture>\n  <!-- Large screens -->\n  <source media=\"(min-width: 800px)\" srcset=\"hero-large.jpg\" />\n  \n  <!-- Medium screens -->\n  <source media=\"(min-width: 400px)\" srcset=\"hero-medium.jpg\" />\n  \n  <!-- Small screens / fallback -->\n  <img src=\"hero-small.jpg\" alt=\"Hero image\" />\n</picture>\n```\n\n## Track Element (Subtitles)\n\nAdd captions to videos:\n\n```html\n<video controls>\n  <source src=\"movie.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n  \n  <!-- Subtitles -->\n  <track\n    kind=\"subtitles\"\n    src=\"subtitles-en.vtt\"\n    srclang=\"en\"\n    label=\"English\"\n    default\n  />\n  \n  <track\n    kind=\"subtitles\"\n    src=\"subtitles-es.vtt\"\n    srclang=\"es\"\n    label=\"Spanish\"\n  />\n</video>\n```\n\n## Complete Media Gallery Example\n\n```html\n<section class=\"media-gallery\">\n  <h2>Media Gallery</h2>\n  \n  <!-- Featured Video -->\n  <figure class=\"featured-video\">\n    <video controls poster=\"video-thumb.jpg\" width=\"640\">\n      <source src=\"demo.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n      <source src=\"demo.webm\" type=\"video/webm\" />\n      Your browser doesn't support HTML video.\n    </video>\n    <figcaption>\n      Product Demo: See our features in action\n    </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  \n  <!-- Audio Player -->\n  <figure>\n    <audio controls>\n      <source src=\"podcast.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\" />\n      <source src=\"podcast.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\" />\n    </audio>\n    <figcaption>Episode 1: Getting Started</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  \n  <!-- Image with Caption -->\n  <figure>\n    <img\n      src=\"team.jpg\"\n      alt=\"Our development team\"\n      width=\"800\"\n      loading=\"lazy\"\n    />\n    <figcaption>Our amazing team of developers</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  \n  <!-- Embedded YouTube -->\n  <figure>\n    <iframe\n      width=\"560\"\n      height=\"315\"\n      src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EXAMPLE\"\n      title=\"Tutorial Video\"\n      allowFullScreen\n      loading=\"lazy\"\n    ></iframe>\n    <figcaption>Watch our getting started tutorial</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n</section>\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n1. **Always provide fallback content** - Text for browsers that don't support the element\n2. **Use multiple formats** - MP4, WebM, Ogg for broad compatibility\n3. **Optimize file sizes** - Compress videos and images\n4. **Use lazy loading** - `loading=\"lazy\"` for below-fold media\n5. **Include captions** - For accessibility and SEO\n6. **Set dimensions** - Prevents layout shift while loading"
